          <LEXSenses>
            <LEXSense LanguageCode="en" LastEdited="2021-02-04 21:40:49" LastEditedBy="">
              <DefinitionLong/>
              <DefinitionShort>(an idiom, literally: to throw a sickle) to begin to harvest a crop by cutting ripe grain with a sickle</DefinitionShort>
