              </Glosses>
              <Comments>In {S:06601401600004} and {S:06601401900004} this idiom occurs in a figurative context, and therefore it may be necessary in some languages to speak of ‘harvesting’ rather than using a phrase which mentions the literal use of a sickle.</Comments>
